short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Cross off vehicles that you have looked at already.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
When searching for a vehicles, you often find yourself looking at the same cars multiple times, forgetting why you didn't like it.

This extension lets you mark vehicles as "read" so you don't waste time.
